00:23:59,860 --> 00:24:00,740
Lari!

256
00:27:08,710 --> 00:27:10,180
(6.3 km, jalan tambahan Lingkaran Kedua Selatan)
Xiaoxing, Xiaoxing.

257
00:27:10,180 --> 00:27:12,220
- Kapten Xu.
- Xiaoxing, 12 km

258
00:27:12,220 --> 00:27:12,980
di barat laut anda,

259
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:14,250
ada beberapa ladang agropelancongan.

260
00:27:14,250 --> 00:27:15,370
Bawa orang untuk periksa kawasan itu.

261
00:27:15,620 --> 00:27:16,500
Faham.

262
00:27:17,820 --> 00:27:18,660
(Menunggu)

263
00:27:20,080 --> 00:27:21,180
(6 km, jalan tambahan Lingkaran Kedua Selatan)

264
00:27:21,180 --> 00:27:23,490
Xu Xiaocong, 8 km di timur anda,

265
00:27:23,490 --> 00:27:24,930
ada stesen bas jarak jauh.

266
00:27:26,940 --> 00:27:27,940
Wang Zhi,

267
00:27:27,940 --> 00:27:29,810
8 atau 9 km di tenggara anda,

268
00:27:30,220 --> 00:27:32,360
ada kawasan perumahan yang sedang diubah suai.

269
00:27:32,360 --> 00:27:33,610
Bawa beberapa orang lagi bersama anda.

270
00:27:35,420 --> 00:27:36,300
Xiao Qiang,

271
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:37,980
7 km di barat daya anda,

272
00:27:38,250 --> 00:27:39,730
ada taman hutan kecil.

273
00:27:39,730 --> 00:27:40,650
Ada bukit dan air di situ.

274
00:27:40,680 --> 00:27:42,380
Kapten Xu, balai polis terima laporan.

275
00:27:42,380 --> 00:27:43,260
6 km ke barat daya,

276
00:27:43,260 --> 00:27:44,520
ada kilang pemprosesan arang batu.

277
00:27:44,520 --> 00:27:45,380
Siapa boleh pergi ke sana?

278
00:27:45,380 --> 00:27:46,460
Kami terlalu jauh dari sana.

279
00:27:46,770 --> 00:27:47,650
Kami di sini.

280
00:27:48,860 --> 00:27:50,660
Kami akan ke sana. Sertai kami segera.

281
00:27:50,660 --> 00:27:51,540
Faham.

282
00:27:52,330 --> 00:27:53,530
Saya kenal kilang ini.

283
00:27:54,090 --> 00:27:55,260
Ia sudah lama ditinggalkan.

284
00:27:55,770 --> 00:27:57,610
Ayah saya kata kerja di sini dulu

285
00:27:57,610 --> 00:27:58,980
ibarat ada mangkuk nasi emas.

286
00:27:59,180 --> 00:28:00,530
Ia sudah lama ditutup.

287
00:28:01,730 --> 00:28:02,610
Baiklah.

288
00:28:03,180 --> 00:28:04,060
Mari kita periksa.

289
00:28:27,460 --> 00:28:28,980
Kau perlukan saksi, kan?

290
00:28:30,220 --> 00:28:32,030
Kalau tidak, orang lain akan fikir kau gila.

291
00:28:35,730 --> 00:28:36,900
Kau boleh ikat aku.

292
00:28:37,310 --> 00:28:38,220
Mudah saja untuk menghapuskan aku,

293
00:28:38,220 --> 00:28:39,220
di mana-mana, bila-bila masa.

294
00:28:48,420 --> 00:28:49,300
Pusing belakang.

295
00:29:55,330 --> 00:29:57,260
Bukankah kamu di sini untuk menyaksikan keabadian aku?

296
00:29:58,220 --> 00:29:59,370
Aku akan tunjukkan kepada kamu.

297
00:30:27,330 --> 00:30:28,210
Masuk.

298
00:36:21,820 --> 00:36:22,700
Wang Bingde,

299
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:24,940
pernahkah kamu terfikir

300
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:26,420
bahawa "teknik keabadian" ini

301
00:36:26,420 --> 00:36:27,300
mungkin palsu?

302
00:36:27,940 --> 00:36:29,610
Tiada makhluk abadi.

303
00:36:29,940 --> 00:36:31,900
Tiada siapa yang boleh hidup selama-lamanya.

304
00:36:36,110 --> 00:36:37,190
Apa yang kamu rancang untuk lakukan?

305
00:36:44,460 --> 00:36:45,340
Wang Bingde!

306
00:36:49,940 --> 00:36:51,050
Walaupun kamu mengambil nyawanya,

307
00:36:51,460 --> 00:36:52,940
itu tidak akan memberimu keabadian.

308
00:37:07,210 --> 00:37:08,250
Wang... Wang Bingde.

309
00:37:09,820 --> 00:37:10,700
Wang Bingde!

310
00:37:29,460 --> 00:37:31,090
Kau tak lepaskan Ding Dang

311
00:37:31,690 --> 00:37:33,730
kerana tanda yang belum selesai itu.

312
00:37:37,050 --> 00:37:37,980
Wang... Wang Bingde,

313
00:37:38,260 --> 00:37:40,900
tak ada teknik keabadian.

314
00:37:44,050 --> 00:37:46,130
Itu semua hanyalah helah

315
00:37:46,490 --> 00:37:47,380
yang dilakukan oleh ahli sihir

316
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:48,570
seperti Liu Chuan.

317
00:38:15,340 --> 00:38:16,220
Wang Bingde,

318
00:38:17,010 --> 00:38:17,940
lepaskan kami.

319
00:39:11,210 --> 00:39:12,090
Dafei.

320
00:39:12,780 --> 00:39:13,780
Dafei,

321
00:39:13,780 --> 00:39:15,460
periksa jika ada jalan keluar lain.

322
00:40:30,340 --> 00:40:31,220
Wang Bingde!

323
00:40:31,980 --> 00:40:32,860
Xu Xiao.

324
00:41:05,610 --> 00:41:06,490
Ding Dang.

325
00:41:07,420 --> 00:41:08,420
Wang Bingde,

326
00:41:08,420 --> 00:41:09,300
berhenti melawan!

327
00:42:12,371 --> 00:42:16,521
