329
00:42:22,551 --> 00:42:26,741
♪Kita terperangkap di sini, merayau tanpa arah♪

330
00:42:27,041 --> 00:42:31,531
♪Tak mampu melepaskan diri sendiri♪

331
00:42:32,751 --> 00:42:38,101
